theme_override_font_sizes/font_size = 22
text = "You look around you. There is nothing but death.

A clarity comes. You wonder how many you killed.

What was the purpose? What did you gain from this — all that is left is bones.

Did you actually save the world? Were they even corrupt in the first place?

All you were doing was listening to Pip.

...At least Pip is happy."
